snippet.textDisplay:
Any anime heads that can point me in the direction of some new material?
Some of my favorites are Neon Genesis Evangelion, Dragon Ball, Attack on Titan, One Punch Man, My Hero Academia, Mob Psycho 100, Psycho-Pass, Special 7: Special Crime Investigation Unit, Assassination Classroom, Cowboy Bebob, Legend of the Galactic Heroes: Die Neue These, Black Clover.
I guess mostly stories that dive into the psyche, with some comedy sometimes. I usually avoid the series with multiple hundreds of episodes because it's just so much time to catch up. Dragon Ball being the exception because I've watched it since I was a child, and Black Clover since I've already been watching since premier.
